Evidey unveils the mystery of a man missing through the story of a woman and her family in an intense search.

Two Schools - one for the rich and one for the poor. Two rival gangs. Two rebel leaders and their epic tale of romance, rivalry and friendship. Prof. John Abraham, who guides these youngsters as they step from adolescence to adulthood.
A simple love story between a man and his wife is broken by a series of unfortunate events.

Mathai's kindness and simplicity endeared him to everyone around him. When an unfortunate turn of events land Mathai in trouble, the people whose life he touched with his kindness rally around to help him.

Geetha, Suni's wife, bears the brunt of his negligent lifestyle and often quarrels with him over it. After witnessing a gruesome accident, Suni and his friends find their lives taking some really unexpected turns.

Sachin's father named him after the great Sachin Tendulkar. So, just like Tendulkar when he falls for a girl older than him, the youngster starts believing that perhaps he shares a lot more in common with his idol than just a name.

An extraordinary journey of a small town boy, Shibu who aspires to be a film-maker. While working on his career path, he meets a girl, Kalyani, who supports his dreams. What follows is how their aspirations bring them together.

Cops of Paramedu Police Station encounter a series of events while they are on a mission to improve the image of Kerala Police, by making it people friendly. Will they become successful in their mission?
A rom-com based in a school where a schoolteacher named Ravi Padmanabhan comes into the lives of Jason and his friends.

Vinayan, an orphan who hard works to accomplish an identity of his own. His buddy in life Smapath who for all time follow him is the only consolation in his life. Vinayan who dream of a ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
Crooked intellect father makes a plan for his son's marriage to a divorced millionaire. Problem begins when son finds out he has erectile dysfunction at his first night

Due to an unfortunate event, Shanthanu leaves home and resides in the outskirts of the city named Ashramam Veedu. During the stay period, there is a twist of fate in Shanthanu's life as he encounters a chain of mysterious events.
Three college-going friends land into trouble when a simple issue that could have been reconciled in a peaceful manner ends up in a fight.

Stories of two strangers, Kuttiyappan and Giri, and how the relationship with their respective daughters brings them closer. The portrayal of their connection throws light on a socially relevant issue.
The police are on the trail of a serial killer, but with the victims being fellow officers, will they be able to catch the killer and solve the case in time?

Sachidanadan had to go to the juvenile home for killing someone. After his release, the recent things that happened to his family, shock Sachidanandan and he has to fight against a powerful drug racket in the city.
Nayana was cheated by her prospective fiancee, but when he does the same to a dear friend, she decides enough is enough

Movie revolves around the annual Onam celebration, happening in a police residential quarter. It offers a unique sneak peek into the everyday life's of police personnel and their family, covering their little joy and sorrows.
A ruthless moneylender must tackle a wicked man's plan to outsmart his way out of the debt to achieve what's rightfully his.

The film tells the story of Eanasu, an old man of ethics, who is in constant struggle with people around him, including his only son Sunny on moral grounds. He surpasses his solitude with ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»

Rishi Ram and his sister Rithu Ram, both of whom are martial arts instructors settled in Rishikesh. Their peaceful life is turned chaotic when they cross paths with a notorious martial arts gang, leading to a spree of furious violence.
The robbery attempt at Chacko Mappila's house goes wrong and Chacko gets murdered. S.I Gireesh, who was out jogging comes to the crime scene by chance and starts his investigation.

A police officer is found raped and murdered but political machinations force the investigating team to act in a manner which denies justice to the family. The search for the culprits takes the team to the borderlands of India and China.

Aravind is informed that something unexpected has happened to his family and has to reach the hospital immediately. What awaits him comes as a shock as he is soon sucked into a miasma of questions that he has to fight to find the answers.
Guathamante Radham revolves around Gauthamam and his journey of getting a driving license and, for the first time in the family, a car of his own.

Three friends, all the way from their school days and are still together, working in the same company. The problems start when the trio decided to celebrate their colleague's birthday at the place where he stays as a paying guest.

The film tells the story of a village woman named as Devi, her battle against fate and society, certain incidents in her life turned her daily job to burn the corpses, but according to the ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»

Neena is a French teacher and single parent to Nikitha, who is obsessed with the concept of arranged marriage. Their lives change when a retired army man and another young man come to stay at their apartment.
The story revolves around the clash between Ayyappan, a senior police officer who serves at the Attappadi Police Station and Havildar Koshi, who comes to the village with a motive.
A disheartened motivational speaker gets hired by a corporate to become a preacher until his live stint on television puts him and his service under the scanner.

Christians believe that marriages are made in heaven. It is a satirical take on the belief, which is reinforced through marriage rituals, about the Christian marriage and the reality of it as seen around us.

Samuel uses his forensic skills and discovers breakthroughs in a serial killing case as further victims are added to the list. Shikha teams up with Samuel and uncovers evidence that might lead to the killer's identity.

After a village in Kerala is flooded, A scheduled caste family which doesn't get any support from government migrates to Himachal Pradesh in search of job & struggles to adapt in a totally new environment conditions.

Ahammed and Anna are friends from childhood and their parents are also good friends. Both of them who loved each other belonged to extremely religious families. One day, all of a sudden ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
Portraying the impact of the medium of cinema on the minds of children.
The ghost of Isha, who was murdered by a few powerful men, possesses the body of a girl in a family that moves to a hill station bungalow. Isha is out there to take vengeance.
Set in the village areas of Wayanad, Malappuram and Kannur, Kappela revolves around an ordinary, innocent girl who comes to Kozhikode city from a high range area called Poovarmala.
The story revolves around two families, portraying their relationship, and how a hen and its eggs changes it over time.
Love FM revolves around a radio that plays a crucial role in the love story. It is a romantic movie where it touches upon the love stories of two generations.

column4: Shanavas Nazar K P, Jacky S. Kumar
column5: A son, his father and his grandfather lead a happy life in a village in Kerala. One day, a girl from Tamil Nadu comes to their village. Their world turns upside down when she and the son fall in love with each other and decide to elope.
Varky is a quotation Goon who does the dirty work for his Boss and when need be, even for cops. But chaos ensues when his Boss assigns him to kidnap a bride-to-be on the eve of her wedding.

Sujata (mute) is in love with her neighbour, a sufi priest but her father gets her married off to a well-do-to NRI, in Dubai. Ten years have passed since and she thinks that she's left that...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
When his unlucky horoscope doesn't bode well for his future wife, an earnest bachelor goes to surprising lengths to get the family he's always wanted.

Josemon, a young man from Kerala meets Cathy, an American traveler and offers to show her around but during their trip, they begin to share their different views of life to better understand each other.
A software engineer, living in Kerala, is prompted by his family to look for his cousin's missing fiancee. As they stumble upon her video-based suicide note, he races against time to find her.
A family and the various situations navigated by a husband and wife.
A group of friends attempt to make a 'halal' film that conforms to the guidelines and descriptions of an Islamic organization which they are a part of.
The story revolves around a doctor who tries to save his wife when her past haunts her.

Sherin is pursuing a journey through lives of many children's who went through brutal abuses in past. She meets with many stories for her documentary including story of Naseema and Anna which makes U Turn to Sherin's past.

After marriage, a woman struggles to be the submissive wife that her husband and his family expect her to be. The story follows her journey, as she changes herself and, even more so, changes the household.
An alcoholic is left stranded by society, friends and family until he successfully completes his de-addiction. Will they accept him when he is clean and sober?

Razia, who belongs from a conservative town of Kerala, lives happily with her family. During her final year semester, Razia and her friends discuss their desires where she unveils her one wish to fulfill before the end of her student life.
Saajan Bakery Since 1962 revolves around a family-owned bakery that faces sibling rivalry between the two children of the Bakery's founder Saajan.
Three young and not so successful lawyers fight against a social evil.
The story revolves around a group of officers and a series of mysteries, events and cases reported before them in the Cyber Cell. It is also about how they plan and execute their operations.
A gripping tale of an investigation and a family which is threatened by it. Will Georgekutty be able to protect his family this time?
Will cook Babu who shares a deep bond with Kalidasan return to the latter's house after their misunderstanding?
A young crafty man kidnaps his own brother, who has Down Syndrome, from his adoptive parents in an attempt to reclaim his past.
Story about how a woman influences a man and how one can live happily without influence of their desires.
A priest and a police officer are trying to solve a set of mysterious suicides. As their investigation closes in, they discover another crime with even farther-reaching consequences.
Bobby is a young man who goes to a seminary in Goa to become a priest, despite his family opposes that. But something happens during his journey so that he ends it there and returns home.

Faiza joins Delhi University as a research student. She gets acquainted with Amal and other students with a sharp political stance. However, the dynamics of campus life take new forms after the killing of her roommate's brother.
An enigmatic story of an innocent friendship between Koyakutty, an orphan devout Muslim and his childhood friend Jamaal who values his friend more than himself.

Mohan Kumar is an ex-superstar, and Krishnan Unni is his greatest fan and also his driver. The film depicts the lengths that Krishnan Unni and Mohan Kumar's family and friends go to, in order to keep him happy--no matter what it takes.

It is the story about a man told through the viewpoints of various others. His name is Yosuf in the story. The man from Kerala, India lives in UAE for 30 years. He touches the lives of many through his simple words and actions.
A campus full of stupid students. The film is about the story of a Muslim girl coming from an Orthodox family and then an eventful event.
A psychological thriller that revolves around Shaji who faces an intriguing conflict with the many layered shades of human behavior.

Story of Kadakkal Chandran, the Chief Minister of Kerala whose uncompromising attitude towards corruption and his dictatorial actions have gained him a lot of enemies. The events get more intense when he faces an allegation.
An anthology film that takes you through three different eras in the history of Kerala with three different stories.
The movie chronicles the life of Khadeeja, a married Muslim woman confined within the four walls of the household, forced to conceal her desires in the name of religious and societal norms.
The film is based on the misdeeds of a friend who arrives at Mathew's uninvited wedding
The life of Abhinandhan, an ardent devotee of Lord Krishna, turns upside down after a stranger arrives to meet him.

A happy-go-lucky Antony disappoints his Dad who was a teacher, so his Dad brings home 2 puppies to insult Antony and show him how thankful Dogs are. Antony despises the Dogs and never leaves any chances to trouble them.

Shirley and Roy in the middle of an impending Covid lock-down and a personal financial crisis, leave their Mumbai home for Shirley's home in Pala where her father Ittyavira stays. Roy soon finds that her home is not what he thought it is.
When a car breakdown forces a couple to seek shelter in a nearby home, conversations with the stranger inside soon suggest there's a killer among them.
The story of a poor family, a father, mother and two children live happily in a beautiful valley. Adversities affect them. But they overcome them with their true faith and fine deeds.

Joji, an engineering dropout and the youngest son of a rich family lives with his aspirations of becoming super wealthy. Driven by greed and blind ambition, he decides to execute his plans following an unexpected event in the family.

Three police officers who are on a run for life, escaping the outbreak against them due to the unlawful arrest and torture of a civilian. It brings in a few shades of arrogant yet very much human police officers and their helplessness.
An ambitious young woman faces a supernatural force through technology. Will she be able to survive the onslaught and solve this unheard phenomenon?

John Baby, who is recouping from a traumatic accident, meets Nitin, a young boy who interests him with murder stories. When Baby explores the possibility of Nitin's stories by mapping the events, it matches with the real-time incidents.
Unni, a male nurse, is known for reciting horror stories in a captivating manner. But one such recitation turns his life upside down.

Malayalam Feature Film based on the Indian tag sport Kho-Kho. The film is written and directed by Rahul Riji Nair and is produced by First Print Studios. Rajisha Vijayan plays the central protagonist in the film.
When the police try to unravel the truth behind a series of mysterious crimes in a locality, they face an unexpected situation.
Two months have passed since three youngsters belonging to a political outfit have gone missing. C.I Srikanth aided by C.P Aby Mathew are given a final two days to solve the mystery.
Ameera tells the story of an inter caste married couple and incidents happening to their children after they pass away.

column4: Jayesh Mohan, Shajan Kallai, Anu Kurisinkal, Shanoob Karuvath, Sreejith Chandran, Fawaz Mohamed
column5: There are six short films in this movie, each painting different shades of love.
The story revolves around the life of a couple Roy and Tina whose happy life lands into an unsettling loop of twists when a doubt about Roy's identity haunts Tina.

The film tells the riveting story of a complex murder case, parallelly investigated by a police officer and an investigative journalist in their own way, who eventually cross paths to unravel secrets they never imagined.
Associate director Sara, is struggling to do her first project. Will she be able to succeed with her decisions and get things right?
A past ridden with crime, death and pain is recounted to Freddy, a juvenile criminal, who has been assigned to eliminate his estranged uncle Sulaiman, an aging patriarch, while behind bars.

The mystery revolves around 5 young people in a hill station resort. Something starts to haunt them without revealing it's presence, while it creates a death trap for them.Will they make it out alive?

A young vulnerable woman who gets caught up in the abduction of a group of school girls, by an armed and dangerous gang of goons becomes the only hope of their survival, while the police ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
Conflicts started to happen in Moosa Khader's home after the entry of a police officer and a murder convict.
Oliver Twist (Indrans) wants to be tech-savvy and become a better companion to his two sons, who spend more time on their phones than with their loved ones.
A day in the life of a junior architect and the people he interacts with.
Varthik, a student in one of the campuses of Chennai, one day happens to see an extraordinary sight in the college library. He witnesses Jency Jaison, a college senior in a mysterious situation.

Dpt. Tahsildar Paul Mathai arrives in town for some court matters. He is welcomed by his son-in-law Allen. But when Paul is leaving Allen's home, something catches his eye. There comes the shift in their lives...
Sunny loses everything that he earned in his life. Shattered and hopeless, he smuggles himself back from Dubai to Kerala in midst of a global pandemic with his own secret plans.
Sam, an ace pianist and a pretentious blind man accidentally gets thrown into a famous yesteryear celebrity's homicide which turns his life upside down.

Star is about a couple, Roy (Joju) and Ardra (Sheelu). Married for 17 years and living happily with their children, their life turns upside down once Ardra, a homemaker, encounters some eerie situations.
Set in Kanjahad, film narrates through the day before a traditional marriage engagement party Suja and Laxmikanth, fixed by Suja's father against her wishes.

In Munnar, understudies are seized by transport gangsters who come on visit and snatch understudies on the vehicle and move towards the Munnar forest. Police are endeavoring to get the ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»

The film revolves around a single day in 'Hill Top' - the once-grand, now-drab hotel in downtown Ernakulam, where a constantly bickering married couple, Pavithran and Haripriya, checks-in for a jolly stay. All the hotel employees and residents seem odd from the beginning itself. Then, all of a sudden, a resident shows up dead under some mysterious circumstances. Now, everyone's a suspect.

Two undercover cops who go in search of a fugitive enter another dimension occupied by uncivilized residents who are crass and rude. There, the two men get stuck in an apparent time loop as inexplicable events begin to occur.
Kurup is a criminal who is on the run from police after murdering someone for life insurance fraud.

Chacko sir's dream of becoming Chief Minister of Kerala get scattered when his daughter elope and marry a comrade from opposition. This political satire drama focuses on the newly married young couples having different political views
Aaha is a sports drama film based on the game tug of war.

Joy Mon plans his own birthday party to overcome sadness and loneliness, but things take an unpleasant turn when the man next to his friend's house become deceased. Can Joy Mon have a pleasant and cheerful birthday celebration ?
Working as a housekeeper cum escort, Sumitra trudges along with her uneventful life in a resort at a hill station in Kerala. Haunted with self-pity, she finds solace in alcohol.
Sara's husband Tom gets food-poisoned after a birthday party, and police suspect it was a deliberate attempt to murder him. And they are after the culprit.

Thamban and Antony were best friends and business partners. A family tragedy and its falling-out separates them for good. But now Antony and his family faces a grievous situation, and he is forced to ask his old friend for help.

column1: Marakkar: Lion of the Arabian Sea
column5: Set in the 16th century, the story of Kunjali Marakkar IV, the naval chieftain of the Zamorin of Calicut, and his organization of India's first-ever naval defense against European forces.
Bheeman realizes the inconvenience caused by an old pathway when he had to take his mother to the hospital. His life takes an interesting turn when he decides to broaden the pathway.

Indhu (Salim Kumar) as a drunkard lazy father and Praveena the Mom narrates atypical mallu drunkard family life. She is the breadwinner of family. Being Jobless teenagers Sumesh & Ramesh roam around like their father & careless .
The events that happen in the life of Ani after he gets convicted for a murder.

Aranjali is all set to celebrate the annual temple festival. Some unforeseen chain of events involving an elephant, a few young men, a notorious criminal, a drama troop and some trouble-loving villagers brings complete mayhem to the place.
An unusual event creates a lightning which in turns gives superhuman abilies to an ambitious tailor ,whose responsibility is now to protect his home village from the evil plans of the antagonist.
Kunjeldho, an undergraduate student, falls in love with his classmate Nivedita. Problems arise when Nivedita gets pregnant.
Married couple Dasthakeer and Sulekha move to Dubai with their three children for a better life.
Sabu, Thaju, Ravi and others wait for their loved ones to be treated at a government hospital. Despite their sadness about loved ones, they help each other while learning from each other's lives.

Based on real incidents of the demolition of 'illegally constructed' Maradu flats, Vidhi weaves in two stories; apart from the real-life flat demolition, there is a story of Wayanad tribal colony murders and police atrocities.

Keshu, a 60 year old driving tutor, and his family, flags off a journey to Rameswaram in order to complete his late father's final rituals. Something unforeseen happens en route, which changes his life.
Follows the challenges in the life of a youngster, and events that change his life.

Sharanya, a shy and introverted person, is a native of Kollengode, Palakkad who moves to Thrissur to pursue engineering. She finds it difficult to cope with her new surroundings in college and her hostel.

Randu is a socio-political satire that hilariously portrays how the quite normal life of a village youth namely Vava is disturbed by the acts of some communal groups in the village. The ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»

An under trial patient escapes from hospital. Karthik, the doctor in charge faces disciplinary action. Karthik takes his girl friend to enjoy his youthful life to the new remote place. But there is something else in store.
Mechanic Jayakrishnan gets into a big land deal, as a good business investment, but ends up faced with life-changing situations in making the deal happen.
Investigation story on the murder of a leading criminal lawyer in the city by an IPS officer.
The emotional journey of Arun, his carefree bachelor days in engineering college, and how he matures through various phases of life.
Following the death of a family member, a mother and son experience mysterious events which distort their sense of reality and make them question their sanity.
The plot revolves around the life of a family man. Unexpected events happen in their house. The brother and father decide to take on the challenges.
The happy life of a couple gets affected when things take a new turn.
A larceny leads to murder and Roopesh Raghavan, a young man who has cleared police recruitment tests and awaits posting.

column1: The Arbit Documentation of An Amphibian Hunt: Aavasavyuham
column5: Joy is a man who seems to have a mysterious connection with nature. One day he arrives in Puthuvype, and the people there recount stories about him. No one knows where he came from and no one knows where he was going either.

Kallan D'Souza and his friend, get by in life committing petty thefts. CI Manoj is a corrupt police officer who confiscates a huge amount of hawala money, and plans to pocket a big portion of it with his team, rather than turning it in.
A school teacher, who is 28 years old and in in search for a suitable groom!. She has gone through 31 wedding proposals, but not a single one fell into place.

column4: Kunjila Mascillamani, Jeo Baby, Jithin Issac Thomas, Akhil Anilkumar, Francies Louis
column5: An Anthology movie based on Five stories. Each story reveals the necessity of freedom for different individuals in the society.
Neyyattinkara Gopan, an influential goon is stepping in to help Edathala Mathai do an illegal conversion of an 18-acre paddy field. But is he really who he says he is?

column4: Aby Treesa Paul, Anto Jose Periera
column5: Rameshan, a youngster brought up in a middle class family, accidentally enters politics. Will he make it big as a politician?
Former rowdy jayan is in a mission to conduct the marriage of his niece.Things got out of hands when things get worse
Karthi and Sidhu live with their mother. As a family, how they face life and deal with all the challenges thrown at them is what forms the crux of the story.

Michael helms his ancestral family in Kochi, inspiring fear and respect through his past. When a few younger members of the household find his power over their lives too aggravating, they join hands with foes to clamp down on him.
Naradan is a dramatic journey of Chandraprakash, a popular news anchor in the media world who is desperate to prove his worth.

All the governments that have ruled the nation made laws that denied the indigenous people their way of life and their land often, protecting crony capitalist interests. The film revisits an episode of dissent in the 90s which brought up this question amongst us. A history forgotten!

A young couple working are out on a drive where they meet with an accident. It leaves them in a triangle between a cop who investigates the accident and the corrupt political hegemony who are in pursuit of them.
S.I Aravind Karunakaran, a police officer on voluntary leave, is haunted by an old case he investigated. How far will he go to unravel the mystery and bring the truth to light?
Too busy with jobs, three siblings lose their connection to their family. Reuniting for their mom's death anniversary, will her last wish bring back lost love?

Pathrose is a gas agency employee whose family includes his wife and his four children. The central character in the film is his second son Tony, who lives happily without doing any work. ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
The life of a bold middle-class woman who is a boat conductor. She must face shocking events and she fights to survive the trauma, but things take a deadly turn.

The plot revolves around what happens to Clara and Sam four hours a day. Sam's friend Vaishakh offers his owner the opportunity to work as a carrier for the smuggling gang. For the first ...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
An ingenious cop, Nanda Kishore, sets out to untangle a string of mysterious murders in Kochi. As the secrets unveil themselves, he finds himself in a dilemma.
Nandu wishes to be a director like the renowned Malayalam film director, Lal Jose.
The life story of a young Krishnan transforming into a sensible 'grown-up,' over a handful of episodes from different stages in his life.
The journey of Balu, a boy with speech difficulties, who is part of a musical family grows up to conquer his problems. The movie is a nostalgic musical family entertainer.

A Convent in a scenic high range. A rugged mother superior of the convent. The inmates, Sister Elsitta and Sister Jaseentha, percieive Jesus Christ in two ideological extremes. The abrasion...                See full summaryÃ‚Â Ã‚Â»
A game that makes you reminisce the good old days of your life, suddenly takes a turn. Will it depend on a mere game of Antakshari?

After investing Rs 1 crore in a business before the pandemic lockdown, David is neck deep in debts and under immense pressure. As his final hope fades, he decided to end his life. But does fate another trick up its sleeve?
As a college professor's brutal murder sparks student unrest, a cop launches an investigation while a lawyer seeks justice in the the courtroom.
A relatable story for many about the hurdles in connecting or reconnecting with a parent after the ties are severed for whatever reason.
A series of murders is happening in the city. With the police failing to solve the case, a team of CBI Officers under CBI officer Sethurama Iyer take up the investigation to resolve the mystery.
Third World Boys is woven around seven youngsters who set off on an impromptu trip over a weekend. There are no romantic female leads in the movie.
An irreversible moment - A mother loses her son..P. A desperate trial of fostering - Even motherhood goes under threat. - Finally realises no one can be replaced.
A gripping thriller with focus on the relationship between a father and son, and the underlying family dynamics and trust issues that follow.
When a police officer's hunt for a convict on the run takes an unexpected turn, a story filled with emotions, fate and revenge unfolds in front of him.
The story of how a few youngsters in a village enjoy their life when the world itself shuts down due to COVID-19 pandemic and how their life fell apart after an unexpected event happened.
A radio jockey loses his voice all of a sudden due to his chain-smoking habit and he struggles hard to regain his voice. Whether he is successful in his struggle ?
Eleven friends get together for a bachelor party, but the celebrations go awry because of a phone call and a death. A drunk cop steps into unravel the mystery.
Shiny is looking after her bedridden mother-in-law, living along with her father-in-law Kuttichan. Tensions arise pushing Shiny to the point where she cannot take anymore.
Kesh a gifted scientist in the field of AI develops a program called Jack and Jill that can sharpen the physique and mental ability of a person in order to fulfill his father's wish

Radhika Balan, a smart cyber-security expert, advocates the use of the technology for the good but her life is turned upside down when she falls prey to a cyber-stalking incident and her privacy gets compromised.
When the pastor of a local church is murdered, a priest is sent to a problematic village where criminals and criminal activities thrive.
It is about a wronged teacher, who returns to the government school from where he lost his job to guide the students along the right path.
Hitha Das finds alcoholics from in and around Mahi and becomes a refuge for them.

Real-life adaptation of the jewellery robbery that occurred in Kasargod. The case took a 5 member team from the Kerala Police to a dreaded village in Uttar Pradesh where they risked their lives to nab the culprits.

The missing case of a teacher named Prakashan is reported at the police station where John Luther works as a CI. As the investigation progresses, John meets with an accident in a scuffle while investigating another case.
Set in Kunnamkulam, a series of thefts takes place and the Police department is confused over the culprit and the mode of execution. Will they catch the real culprit?
Charly is a reckless youngster who doesn't have any principles concerning relationships. The deeds for his momentary pleasure ends up on a murder, beginning to an unsolvable mystery.

Thirty Five years ago, Matthews and Marry eloped from Southern Kerala and moved to Northern Wayanad. They create a small world for themselves but one day Marry feels sick, and he might have to sell his land to save her. What will he do?
A struggling film actor's life went upside down when two tries to fraud him with the help of technology. How he survives this debacle forms the rest of the story.

Four close friends who live together in Bangalore. The friendship filled with fun and humor which quickly changes into a gripping mystery that keeps the spectators on the edge of their seats and leaves them with mixed feelings.

Sreekuttan is irked and belittled by his townsfolk mockingly calling him Kochaal due to his short stature. His ambition is to become a police officer and decides to prove himself in uniform. Will his dream come true ?
The story of the survival of a tribal student singer. It discusses the neglect and resistance of our society.
Das, who regularly bunks school, is unhappy with his family as they admire his brother for doing well at school. Tragedy strikes when an accident takes place, and at the same time, Das falls in love.

Circle Inspector of Police, Peter Kurishinkal is a stoic and taciturn officer, who prefers brain over brawn to solve his cases. His world is brought upside down when he is assigned a sensational case of homicide.
A courtroom drama in which two talented self made lawyers are determined to win a case where they are on opposing sides.

Viddikalude Mashu is a family drama film about a boy who faces difficulties in life as a result of his inferiority complex. The film portrays how he overcomes numerous obstacles in his life and eventually achieves his life ambition.

Dr. Priyadarshan, a middle class man, silently goes through the pangs of hyperactivity and ADHD that entangles him into a series of coincidental events. He then meets Priscilla, a feisty, constantly doubtful and depressed girl.
While returning from a gang violence, twelve local gangsters are baffled to find a stranger in their van. His presence and actions evokes suspicion. What will happen next?
A fun-filled romantic movie in which two strangers from diverse backgrounds meet on a journey from Ooty to Kerala. The journey advances through different circumstances and coming across new people.

Adithattu denotes the 'lower strata in the society and the fishing community falls under this stratum. Adithattu will also explore the problems and livelihood of the fishermen community and will be a thriller subject.
The movie revolves around a Fort Kochi-based dance troupe named Santacruz. when a Director whose last films were flops, ask his script writer to listen and write the story of Santacruz team.
The film is set in the late 90s revolving around the life of a young high range rubber planter from Mundakayam and his rivalry with a high ranking officer in the Kerala Police.
PAKA is a tale of a river that swells with the blood of two feuding families and a young couple that tries to overcome this hatred with their love.
Story of two young siblings compassion for each other and how they overcome obstacles in life.
An enthusiastic and diligent journalist follows a set of serial murders that rocks her city. She tries to solve the crime not knowing that the murderer could be very close to home.
Follows two police officers at a small wireless police station on the hilltop as they work to resolve the mystery about a woman's body parts that have been scattered all over Elaveezhapoonchira.

The story of renowned psychologist Ravishankar, his wife Padmaja, and some amusing incidents with his clients. Ravishankar and Padmaja, although hailing from a remote village, are residing now in a city and part of the elite society.
Focuses on time travel, fantasy and court proceedings intertwined with emotional and funny moments.

Anikkuttan is an ill-tempered electronics technician who leads a quiet life with his mother. His daily routines are disrupted when his next door neighbor's newborn baby stirs up undesirable memories from his past.
